<ul class="lst-sec-info">
    <li class="last">
        <h4>Pizza Margherita</h4>
        <img class="img_gra" src="http://images.fondnessmedia.com/images/learnaboutpizza.com/Pizza_Margherita_i33.jpg" width="196" height="101" alt="" />
        <p>This is a pizza that is made in accordance to the recipe that was originally made by an Italian chef Raffaelle Esposito. This pizza was made for the first time in the year 1899 when queen Margherita visited Napels. The ingredients that were used in making the pizza were tomatoes, basil, Mozzarella cheese; it was basically an effort to imitate the colors of the flag of Italy. When this pizza was tasted by Queen Margherita, she liked it so much that she wrote a note of thanks to Esposito.</p>
        <a href="http://pizza.gourmetrecipe.com/Pizza_Recipes?search_query=Margherita" class="readmore">Click here</a>
